<br>
This is what I want to avoid<br>
<br>
Mythic: OK let's add a debuff to Flank to help out the Merc<br>
QA: Sounds good, but the infiltrator will also get that, so we better add some testing time to see how it affects the infiltrator into our QA time line<br>
Mythic: Hmmm we don't have that much time, let's just change it for the Merc and not the inf<br>
QA: That's good to, but we'll still have to add some QA time to make sure it hasn't broken the infiltrator.<br>
Dev: And we'll need extra dev time for the additional code changes for doing that<br>
Mythic: Hmmmm, ok let's leave that one for now, it's not a big problem.  OK how can we make savages even better....<br>
<br>
This is the type of discussion I don't want Mythic to be having <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
